    rating: 5,
    date: "Feb 25 2024",
    screenshotUrl: "/images/reviews/ricardoorozco.png",
    transcription: "I have had the pleasure of working with Grecia, an exceptionally talented UX/UI designer whose commitment and attention to detail have been invaluable to our projects. Her ability to dive deep into user needs and translate them into intuitive and elegant design solutions has made a significant difference in the quality of our work. Her dedication to perfecting every aspect of a design—from conceptualization to final implementation—is admirable. Her capacity to collaborate closely with development teams ensures that every project not only meets but exceeds expectations. I highly recommend her for her professionalism, creativity, and for being a key player in the success of our projects.",
