    rating: 5,
    date: "March 8 2024",
    screenshotUrl: "/images/reviews/angelojeda.png",
    transcription: "I am writing this to recommend Grecia, a talented web and UI designer whom I had the pleasure of meeting during our time at university. Grecia has an exceptional eye for detail and a great sense of color that enables her to design any type of website. I have seen Grecia's work first-hand and can attest to her creativity, professionalism, and dedication to her craft. Her designs are not only visually stunning but also highly functional and user-friendly, which is a testament to her ability to understand the needs of both her clients and their audiences. I have no doubt that Grecia's skills and talent would be an asset to any team or project, and I wholeheartedly recommend her to anyone seeking a skilled and reliable web and UI designer",
    reviewUrl: "https://www.linkedin.com/in/grecia-valentina-valero/details/recommendations/",
    projectUrl: "",
    tags: ["UI/UX", "Web Design", "University Projects"],
  },
  {
    id: 3,
    platform: "Fiverr",
    platformColor: "#1DBF73",
    clientName: "Bharat K.",
    clientLocation: "USA",
    rating: 5,
    date: "Oct 2025",
    screenshotUrl: "/images/reviews/testimonial1.png",
    transcription: "Grecia was able to understand our concept and developed the website according to our theme and well-written documentation with great user flow.",
    reviewUrl: "https://www.fiverr.com/s/rE4LEvP",
    projectUrl: "/portfolio/projects/anywhere-healing-wellness-website-astro",
